{"tid":1611230,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"文宣、集會、遊行係非常重要!","createTime":"2019-10-02T01:56:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-02T02:02:50.000Z","uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fde36a64567d8662b96ebde290046593fcdf575b","tid":1611230,"uid":236646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T01:56:16.000Z","msg":"麻煩大家善用連登平台,，作為行動宣傳平台。<br />\n唔好再推垃圾文，直接比負評然後用不推文功能。<br />\n以達到宣傳效果，依家好明顯好多警狗同埋五毛不斷出垃圾POST。<br />\n取代大量行動POST，令到宣傳大減，從而令運動氣氛漸減咁。<br />\n大家討論垃圾文係無助呢場運動，行動先係最實際!<br />\n與其討論垃圾文，不如討論番點樣先可以改革成功、運動成功更加實在!<br />\n<br />\n依家已經去到實彈階段，希望大家做鍵盤戰士都要方向正確。<br />\n仲有，外國戰線係非常重要!重要!重要!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n只係得本土係無法成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依家已經毫無退路, 一退 香港市民將會成為三等公民<br />\n大家都有眼見，香港人係出街比黑警、藍絲狗叫做曱甴<br />\n年輕人出街就係原罪, 會比人拉、鎖、塔、打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n依家無尊嚴個班唔係佢地，而係一眾香港市民呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家鍵盤係最壞的時代必須發揮作用! 作為一眾巴打強大支援!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"214e94e0906024a69599a27513514fa2aac6af0c","tid":1611230,"uid":160842,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-02T02:02:50.000Z","msg":"今日12點半，黑西裝癱瘓全中環！！！！！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1610862\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1610862</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNCe3Qz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNCe3Qz.jpg&h=978efe31&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H6QXhaz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2